---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import "../styles/about.css";

const pageTitle = "About";
---

<BaseLayout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
  <header class="about-hero">
    <h1 class="title">关于</h1>
    <p>这个网站使用 <strong>Astro</strong> 构建</p> 
    <p>关于主题，可以看看这里 <a class="post-link" href="/posts/tech/astro-pudding/">astro-pudding</a> 或者访问我的 GitHub。</p>
  </header>

  <main class="about-container">
    <section class="projects-section">
      <div class="projects-grid">
        <article class="project-card card">
          <div class="iframe-wrapper">
            <iframe src="https://huamurui.github.io/photo-viewer/" title="照片" loading="lazy"></iframe>
          </div>
          <div class="project-actions"><a class="post-link" href="https://huamurui.github.io/photo-viewer/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在新标签页打开</a></div>
        </article>

        <article class="project-card card">
          <div class="iframe-wrapper">
            <iframe src="https://huamurui.github.io/html-s/" title="HTML 示例" loading="lazy"></iframe>
          </div>
          <div class="project-actions"><a class="post-link" href="https://huamurui.github.io/html-s/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在新标签页打开</a></div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <aside class="quote-section">
      <p>痛苦如此持久，像蜗牛充满耐心地移动；快乐如此短暂，像兔子的尾巴掠过秋天的草原。</p>
    </aside>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>